  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 9.59,
      "text": "Screen English"
    },
    {
      "start": 9.59,
      "end": 30.32,
      "text": "타막 없이 영화를 볼 수 있는 그날까지"
    },
    {
      "start": 30.32,
      "end": 31.88,
      "text": "Screen English Time"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.88,
      "end": 33.98,
      "text": "10월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 33.98,
      "end": 35.54,
      "text": "After Wedding in New York"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.54,
      "end": 36.74,
      "text": "After the Wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.74,
      "end": 37.12,
      "text": "입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 37.92,
      "end": 38.64,
      "text": "어서오세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 39.02,
      "end": 39.4,
      "text": "Hello."
    },
    {
      "start": 40.2,
      "end": 41.26,
      "text": "굿모닝입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 41.48,
      "end": 42.22,
      "text": "네, 굿모닝."
    },
    {
      "start": 42.98,
      "end": 46.0,
      "text": "오늘 줄리안 모어, 그리고 미셸 월리엠,"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.14,
      "end": 48.38,
      "text": "밀리 크루답, 그리고 이와 같이"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.38,
      "end": 52.88,
      "text": "멋진 연기파 배우들과 함께하는 마지막 시간입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 52.88,
      "end": 57.5,
      "text": "A great cast, the last day, to spend with a great cast."
    },
    {
      "start": 57.56,
      "end": 59.46,
      "text": "여태까지 이렇게 영화를 점검을 해보면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.46,
      "end": 60.62,
      "text": "I was so into it."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.62,
      "end": 64.04,
      "text": "보면 볼수록 더 빠져들게 되는 매력이 있더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 64.24,
      "end": 67.66,
      "text": "It puts you on a roller coaster, full of twists and turns."
    },
    {
      "start": 67.66,
      "end": 69.74,
      "text": "An emotional roller coaster."
    },
    {
      "start": 69.86,
      "end": 75.16,
      "text": "Yeah, I was overwhelmed by the spectacular castings and stories as well."
    },
    {
      "start": 75.24,
      "end": 77.58,
      "text": "You even said you shed some tears?"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.7,
      "end": 77.96,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.02,
      "end": 78.52,
      "text": "A few tears?"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.52,
      "end": 80.36,
      "text": "눈물 진짜 많이 흘렸어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 80.48,
      "end": 81.02,
      "text": "많이."
    },
    {
      "start": 81.04,
      "end": 84.48,
      "text": "이 영화의 후반으로 가면서 계속 울컥울컥해가지고."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.74,
      "end": 86.36,
      "text": "Yeah, I had that moment too."
    },
    {
      "start": 87.1,
      "end": 90.56,
      "text": "특히 저는 이 영화를 카페에서 혼자서 봤거든요."
    },
    {
      "start": 91.1,
      "end": 91.94,
      "text": "All alone?"
    },
    {
      "start": 92.02,
      "end": 92.24,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 92.24,
      "end": 96.24,
      "text": "So what happens when you see an emotional scene"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.24,
      "end": 97.62,
      "text": "and you start tearing up?"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.72,
      "end": 99.52,
      "text": "주변에 있는 다른 분들이 저를 보고"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.52,
      "end": 101.52,
      "text": "어? 저 여자 왜 저래? 이렇게 생각할까봐"
    },
    {
      "start": 101.52,
      "end": 103.42,
      "text": "막 눈물을 애써 참으면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.42,
      "end": 105.52,
      "text": "눈물이 그렁그렁한데"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.52,
      "end": 108.28,
      "text": "막 아닌 척하면서 보느라고 힘들었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 108.48,
      "end": 110.48,
      "text": "I still do that in the movie theater."
    },
    {
      "start": 110.48,
      "end": 111.44,
      "text": "Oh, 그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.56,
      "end": 112.92,
      "text": "Even when I'm just with my wife."
    },
    {
      "start": 113.48,
      "end": 115.86,
      "text": "When you like, you feel this frog in your throat"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.86,
      "end": 117.42,
      "text": "and you feel the tears coming"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.42,
      "end": 120.34,
      "text": "I feel like I have to hold them back."
    },
    {
      "start": 121.68,
      "end": 122.6,
      "text": "재밌는 표현이네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 122.76,
      "end": 124.78,
      "text": "개구리가 목구멍에서 튀어나올 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 124.8,
      "end": 125.96,
      "text": "The frog in your throat."
    },
    {
      "start": 126.12,
      "end": 127.88,
      "text": "딱 비슷한 느낌 뭔지 알 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 127.96,
      "end": 128.66,
      "text": "그 frog."
    },
    {
      "start": 129.32,
      "end": 130.24,
      "text": "Good expression."
    },
    {
      "start": 130.6,
      "end": 133.32,
      "text": "I think anywhere you go, men, especially men,"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.32,
      "end": 135.18,
      "text": "they don't want to show their tears."
    },
    {
      "start": 136.02,
      "end": 139.28,
      "text": "아, 맨이 한 모습을 추구하시네 우리 크쌤이셨습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 139.28,
      "end": 143.36,
      "text": "그래도 왠지 우리 몸속에, 마음속에는"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.36,
      "end": 146.18,
      "text": "왠지 이모셔널한 분이 확실하신 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 146.64,
      "end": 149.24,
      "text": "Yeah. I have some emotions."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.44,
      "end": 153.78,
      "text": "자, 오늘 또 촬영 감독에 관련된 이야기를"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.78,
      "end": 155.08,
      "text": "들려주실 예정이죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.24,
      "end": 159.16,
      "text": "The cinematographer, a man, I believe he's a man named"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.16,
      "end": 161.68,
      "text": "훌리오 마카트, he talked about the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 161.68,
      "end": 164.9,
      "text": "and he talked about working with this all-star cast"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.9,
      "end": 167.52,
      "text": "줄리안 모어, 미셸 윌리엄스, and Billy Crudup."
    },
    {
      "start": 167.52,
      "end": 170.78,
      "text": "He described it as driving a Ferrari."
    },
    {
      "start": 171.28,
      "end": 172.56,
      "text": "You know a Ferrari?"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.82,
      "end": 173.34,
      "text": "외제차?"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.46,
      "end": 173.86,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 173.94,
      "end": 174.42,
      "text": "비싼 거."
    },
    {
      "start": 174.48,
      "end": 176.02,
      "text": "아주 럭셔리ous car이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 176.42,
      "end": 177.54,
      "text": "You start really fast."
    },
    {
      "start": 177.66,
      "end": 180.12,
      "text": "You get up to a high speed really fast."
    },
    {
      "start": 180.18,
      "end": 182.1,
      "text": "기름을 마신다는 이야기가 있습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 182.1,
      "end": 183.08,
      "text": "아, yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 183.56,
      "end": 184.46,
      "text": "기름 먹는 하나."
    },
    {
      "start": 185.75,
      "end": 187.03,
      "text": "Takes up a lot of gas."
    },
    {
      "start": 187.45,
      "end": 188.75,
      "text": "But it was unbelievable."
    },
    {
      "start": 189.53,
      "end": 192.25,
      "text": "Especially Julian, it was so good, he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 192.63,
      "end": 195.77,
      "text": "And I know Julian, but I didn't know Michelle Williams."
    },
    {
      "start": 196.15,
      "end": 198.13,
      "text": "And he got to know her over this movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 198.13,
      "end": 205.89,
      "text": "And one special thing that he mentioned was there was a scene towards the end of the film"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.89,
      "end": 208.09,
      "text": "where Julian loses it."
    },
    {
      "start": 208.73,
      "end": 214.01,
      "text": "You know, she has a disease and she just breaks down emotionally and she starts crying."
    },
    {
      "start": 214.01,
      "end": 221.45,
      "text": "And this guy was behind the camera and he was filming the scene and he actually started tearing up."
    },
    {
      "start": 221.53,
      "end": 224.83,
      "text": "He was weeping, literally weeping through the lens."
    },
    {
      "start": 224.95,
      "end": 227.13,
      "text": "Wow, he cried while filming it."
    },
    {
      "start": 227.33,
      "end": 231.41,
      "text": "And usually a cinematographer, people behind the camera, they don't cry."
    },
    {
      "start": 231.41,
      "end": 234.31,
      "text": "Because it's like take one, take two, it's work."
    },
    {
      "start": 234.77,
      "end": 235.75,
      "text": "그냥 일이니까."
    },
    {
      "start": 236.19,
      "end": 239.95,
      "text": "But he actually weeped and he said this had never, ever happened to him before."
    },
    {
      "start": 240.11,
      "end": 240.55,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 240.67,
      "end": 246.27,
      "text": "And he hopes that the audience can feel this kind of intense emotion that he felt behind the camera."
    },
    {
      "start": 246.59,
      "end": 247.03,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 247.59,
      "end": 250.71,
      "text": "제가, I looked up his picture before."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.83,
      "end": 251.19,
      "text": "Oh, you did?"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.45,
      "end": 251.65,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 251.89,
      "end": 253.27,
      "text": "이분의 사진을 한번 찾아봤어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 253.35,
      "end": 254.85,
      "text": "궁금해가지고 어떤 분인지."
    },
    {
      "start": 254.99,
      "end": 255.25,
      "text": "Coolio."
    },
    {
      "start": 255.69,
      "end": 256.01,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 256.17,
      "end": 258.53,
      "text": "He doesn't look like he's going to cry easily."
    },
    {
      "start": 258.53,
      "end": 260.37,
      "text": "He doesn't look like an emotional, sentimental man."
    },
    {
      "start": 260.37,
      "end": 261.73,
      "text": "완전 마초 스타일."
    },
    {
      "start": 262.01,
      "end": 262.29,
      "text": "Ah."
    },
    {
      "start": 262.59,
      "end": 262.89,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 263.25,
      "end": 267.53,
      "text": "쉽게 눈물을 흘릴 것 같아 보이진 않았는데 그럼에도 불구하고 이렇게"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.53,
      "end": 273.53,
      "text": "줄리안 무어의 연기에 감동을 받아가지고 촬영 감독까지도 이렇게 울었다라는 이야기였습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 273.77,
      "end": 274.79,
      "text": "A fine performance."
    },
    {
      "start": 275.01,
      "end": 276.25,
      "text": "Wonderful performance."
    },
    {
      "start": 276.35,
      "end": 277.65,
      "text": "정말 동의합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 278.23,
      "end": 280.39,
      "text": "오늘 장면 먼저 듣고 오겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 281.33,
      "end": 282.71,
      "text": "Why didn't you tell me yourself?"
    },
    {
      "start": 283.07,
      "end": 283.87,
      "text": "You were lying."
    },
    {
      "start": 284.05,
      "end": 286.37,
      "text": "Every minute you knew and you didn't tell me."
    },
    {
      "start": 286.37,
      "end": 286.95,
      "text": "I'm sorry."
    },
    {
      "start": 286.95,
      "end": 288.78,
      "text": "I didn't want to make you sad."
    },
    {
      "start": 288.88,
      "end": 291.1,
      "text": "You didn't think I'd be sad if you just died one day?"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.28,
      "end": 291.64,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "start": 291.84,
      "end": 292.2,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.8,
      "end": 294.28,
      "text": "I didn't want anything to change."
    },
    {
      "start": 294.98,
      "end": 295.78,
      "text": "Maybe I was wrong."
    },
    {
      "start": 296.77,
      "end": 300.95,
      "text": "If I knew that you were dying, I wouldn't have spent my time doing other stuff."
    },
    {
      "start": 301.59,
      "end": 305.63,
      "text": "Oh, 이제 드디어 딸인 그레이스까지 알게 됐어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 305.87,
      "end": 309.13,
      "text": "그래서 그레이스가 테리사의 회사로 찾아왔습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 309.79,
      "end": 312.81,
      "text": "And she told 테리사 how precious she was."
    },
    {
      "start": 313.01,
      "end": 313.25,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.25,
      "end": 313.89,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 314.11,
      "end": 315.65,
      "text": "So everybody knows now."
    },
    {
      "start": 316.17,
      "end": 317.71,
      "text": "The cat is out of the bag."
    },
    {
      "start": 317.71,
      "end": 320.91,
      "text": "They all know that her mom is dying."
    },
    {
      "start": 321.87,
      "end": 322.73,
      "text": "And yeah, she's shocked."
    },
    {
      "start": 323.11,
      "end": 325.27,
      "text": "And she also feels betrayed."
    },
    {
      "start": 325.69,
      "end": 326.77,
      "text": "She wanted to know."
    },
    {
      "start": 327.15,
      "end": 328.81,
      "text": "But her mom didn't tell her."
    },
    {
      "start": 330.45,
      "end": 338.59,
      "text": "충격 속에서도 그래도 가장 소중한 엄마에 대한 그런 자신의 진심을 담아서 이야기하고 있는 장면이에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 339.23,
      "end": 340.89,
      "text": "주요 표현들 점검해 볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 340.89,
      "end": 345.15,
      "text": "Lying every minute."
    },
    {
      "start": 345.47,
      "end": 349.53,
      "text": "여기서는 거짓말하다의 lie에 ing가 붙은 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 349.75,
      "end": 353.15,
      "text": "그래서 철자는 ly ing가 되겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 353.69,
      "end": 354.11,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 354.31,
      "end": 355.55,
      "text": "You lie every minute."
    },
    {
      "start": 356.09,
      "end": 357.99,
      "text": "너는 매 순간 거짓말하지."
    },
    {
      "start": 358.21,
      "end": 359.15,
      "text": "이라는 문장이었고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 359.67,
      "end": 365.35,
      "text": "처음 들으셨던 표현은 lying every minute이었으니까 매 순간 속이는."
    },
    {
      "start": 365.35,
      "end": 366.23,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 366.39,
      "end": 367.41,
      "text": "So she feels betrayed."
    },
    {
      "start": 367.53,
      "end": 369.31,
      "text": "Why were you lying every minute?"
    },
    {
      "start": 370.63,
      "end": 372.67,
      "text": "Didn't want anything to change."
    },
    {
      "start": 372.87,
      "end": 374.65,
      "text": "Didn't want anything to change."
    },
    {
      "start": 375.01,
      "end": 377.83,
      "text": "어느 것도 변하지 않기를 원했다."
    },
    {
      "start": 378.74,
      "end": 380.44,
      "text": "If I knew that you were dying."
    },
    {
      "start": 381.08,
      "end": 383.98,
      "text": "내가 당신이 죽어가는 것을 알았더라면."
    },
    {
      "start": 384.34,
      "end": 386.86,
      "text": "이라는 가정절이 되겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 386.98,
      "end": 388.96,
      "text": "If I knew that you were dying."
    },
    {
      "start": 389.22,
      "end": 391.04,
      "text": "이라는 표현까지 먼저 들어보고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 391.42,
      "end": 392.64,
      "text": "이 내용 다시 한번 들어보겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 392.64,
      "end": 394.46,
      "text": "Why didn't you tell me yourself?"
    },
    {
      "start": 394.88,
      "end": 398.22,
      "text": "You were lying every minute you knew and you didn't tell me."
    },
    {
      "start": 398.28,
      "end": 398.76,
      "text": "I'm sorry."
    },
    {
      "start": 399.43,
      "end": 400.59,
      "text": "I didn't want to make you sad."
    },
    {
      "start": 400.71,
      "end": 402.91,
      "text": "And you didn't think I'd be sad if you just died one day?"
    },
    {
      "start": 403.09,
      "end": 403.47,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "start": 403.65,
      "end": 404.03,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "start": 404.61,
      "end": 406.09,
      "text": "I didn't want anything to change."
    },
    {
      "start": 406.79,
      "end": 407.61,
      "text": "Maybe I was wrong."
    },
    {
      "start": 408.61,
      "end": 410.67,
      "text": "If I knew that you were dying."
    },
    {
      "start": 410.77,
      "end": 412.79,
      "text": "I wouldn't have spent my time doing other stuff."
    },
    {
      "start": 412.79,
      "end": 416.68,
      "text": "그레이스도 참 힘들었을 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 417.98,
      "end": 424.16,
      "text": "아빠로부터 이제 친모의 사실도 원래 돌아가셨다고 알고 있었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 424.16,
      "end": 425.66,
      "text": "자기 눈앞에 나타났죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 425.66,
      "end": 434.2,
      "text": "그리고 이제 테리사가 회복이 불가능한 그런 위중한 병에 걸려서"
    },
    {
      "start": 434.2,
      "end": 437.0,
      "text": "she was dying 하고 있었다라는 것을 깨달았잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 437.0,
      "end": 439.38,
      "text": "And Grace heard this from someone else?"
    },
    {
      "start": 439.52,
      "end": 442.38,
      "text": "Not her special mom?"
    },
    {
      "start": 442.82,
      "end": 444.16,
      "text": "Her adoptive mom?"
    },
    {
      "start": 444.94,
      "end": 445.74,
      "text": "Yeah, who told her?"
    },
    {
      "start": 446.14,
      "end": 448.3,
      "text": "참, 아, 이거는 아빠가 이야기해줬어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 448.38,
      "end": 448.86,
      "text": "Oscar가."
    },
    {
      "start": 448.96,
      "end": 449.38,
      "text": "Oscar."
    },
    {
      "start": 449.62,
      "end": 449.8,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 449.88,
      "end": 451.64,
      "text": "So she, yeah, she's offended."
    },
    {
      "start": 451.96,
      "end": 453.88,
      "text": "Why didn't you tell me yourself?"
    },
    {
      "start": 454.66,
      "end": 456.04,
      "text": "딱 그 말이었죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 456.24,
      "end": 458.82,
      "text": "자, 첫 번째로 그레이스가 한 말 다시 들어보겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 459.48,
      "end": 460.08,
      "text": "바로 그겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 460.24,
      "end": 461.98,
      "text": "Why didn't you tell me yourself?"
    },
    {
      "start": 461.98,
      "end": 463.04,
      "text": "바로 이 말이었죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 463.14,
      "end": 464.72,
      "text": "Why didn't you tell me yourself?"
    },
    {
      "start": 465.22,
      "end": 468.76,
      "text": "아니, 왜 직접 나에게 말씀해주지 않으신 거예요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 469.8,
      "end": 473.34,
      "text": "You were lying every minute you knew and you didn't tell me."
    },
    {
      "start": 473.52,
      "end": 477.68,
      "text": "You were lying every minute you knew and you didn't tell me."
    },
    {
      "start": 477.68,
      "end": 483.14,
      "text": "네네, 그동안 네네 속이고 있다는 것을 알면서도 숨겼던 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 483.96,
      "end": 484.84,
      "text": "I'm sorry."
    },
    {
      "start": 485.22,
      "end": 487.3,
      "text": "테리사가 미안하다고 사과하죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 487.88,
      "end": 489.6,
      "text": "I didn't want to make you sad."
    },
    {
      "start": 489.74,
      "end": 491.22,
      "text": "I didn't want to make you sad."
    },
    {
      "start": 491.22,
      "end": 494.5,
      "text": "나는 너에게 슬프게 만들고 싶지 않았어."
    },
    {
      "start": 495.8,
      "end": 499.48,
      "text": "And you didn't think I'd be sad if you just died one day?"
    },
    {
      "start": 499.68,
      "end": 501.1,
      "text": "응, 그레이스의 말입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 501.32,
      "end": 505.22,
      "text": "And you didn't think I'd be sad if you just died one day?"
    },
    {
      "start": 505.68,
      "end": 507.26,
      "text": "굉장히 논리적이죠, 그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 507.56,
      "end": 512.36,
      "text": "그러다가 어느 날 갑자기 엄마가 떠나버리면 내가 안 슬플 것 같았어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 512.62,
      "end": 513.28,
      "text": "라는 말입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 513.6,
      "end": 513.98,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "start": 514.52,
      "end": 516.76,
      "text": "그랬더니 테리사가, no, 아니야."
    },
    {
      "start": 517.22,
      "end": 517.72,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "start": 517.72,
      "end": 518.72,
      "text": "그럼 뭔데요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 518.72,
      "end": 519.28,
      "text": "뭔데요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 520.78,
      "end": 522.62,
      "text": "Oh, 그 다음 대사네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 522.74,
      "end": 522.94,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 523.2,
      "end": 525.08,
      "text": "내 진심의 반응이기도 하고."
    },
    {
      "start": 525.22,
      "end": 525.9,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "start": 526.28,
      "end": 531.9,
      "text": "Who would not be sad if someone just dropped dead all of a sudden without any warning?"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.7,
      "end": 535.64,
      "text": "I didn't want anything to change."
    },
    {
      "start": 535.96,
      "end": 538.96,
      "text": "나는 아무것도 변하지 않았으면 했거든."
    },
    {
      "start": 539.08,
      "end": 540.94,
      "text": "I didn't want anything to change."
    },
    {
      "start": 541.2,
      "end": 542.22,
      "text": "Maybe I was wrong."
    },
    {
      "start": 542.22,
      "end": 544.32,
      "text": "근데 maybe I was wrong."
    },
    {
      "start": 544.72,
      "end": 546.32,
      "text": "근데 내가 틀렸나봐."
    },
    {
      "start": 546.6,
      "end": 548.84,
      "text": "내가 틀린 생각한 것 같구나."
    },
    {
      "start": 549.34,
      "end": 549.6,
      "text": "Huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 549.78,
      "end": 551.58,
      "text": "I wouldn't know what I would do."
    },
    {
      "start": 551.72,
      "end": 553.36,
      "text": "I would probably tell my family."
    },
    {
      "start": 553.5,
      "end": 553.8,
      "text": "Sure."
    },
    {
      "start": 554.0,
      "end": 555.98,
      "text": "Just when I have a cough or I'm a little sick."
    },
    {
      "start": 556.64,
      "end": 557.4,
      "text": "I'm sick."
    },
    {
      "start": 557.4,
      "end": 557.64,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 557.7,
      "end": 558.54,
      "text": "감기 걸려도."
    },
    {
      "start": 558.8,
      "end": 560.46,
      "text": "Make me some juk, please."
    },
    {
      "start": 561.02,
      "end": 561.54,
      "text": "Come on."
    },
    {
      "start": 561.66,
      "end": 561.98,
      "text": "Juk."
    },
    {
      "start": 563.36,
      "end": 564.68,
      "text": "더 막 생생내고."
    },
    {
      "start": 564.74,
      "end": 565.06,
      "text": "그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 565.86,
      "end": 566.92,
      "text": "그런 스타일이시군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 567.02,
      "end": 568.22,
      "text": "Just for a little sickness."
    },
    {
      "start": 568.4,
      "end": 570.28,
      "text": "아이, 약한 척 살짝 해주는."
    },
    {
      "start": 571.24,
      "end": 572.14,
      "text": "백신 맞고 나서."
    },
    {
      "start": 572.28,
      "end": 573.24,
      "text": "Oh, it hurts."
    },
    {
      "start": 573.36,
      "end": 573.82,
      "text": "Did you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 574.02,
      "end": 574.36,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 574.82,
      "end": 576.46,
      "text": "Please, make me some food."
    },
    {
      "start": 576.62,
      "end": 578.0,
      "text": "How was her reaction?"
    },
    {
      "start": 578.58,
      "end": 580.58,
      "text": "She's like, ah, Chris, get over it."
    },
    {
      "start": 580.74,
      "end": 581.8,
      "text": "You're fine."
    },
    {
      "start": 581.92,
      "end": 584.96,
      "text": "꾀병불이지만 이렇게 강하게 키우시는 스타일이시군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 584.98,
      "end": 585.3,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 585.62,
      "end": 587.54,
      "text": "그놈의 엄살이 심하다."
    },
    {
      "start": 588.1,
      "end": 588.38,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 589.42,
      "end": 591.56,
      "text": "Anyway, this situation is a little more serious."
    },
    {
      "start": 592.6,
      "end": 594.24,
      "text": "But yeah, it's a difficult choice."
    },
    {
      "start": 595.68,
      "end": 600.42,
      "text": "If I knew that you were dying, I wouldn't have spent my time doing other stuff."
    },
    {
      "start": 600.5,
      "end": 609.26,
      "text": "If I knew that you were dying, 내가 엄마가 아픈 줄 알았더라면, I wouldn't have spent my time doing other stuff."
    },
    {
      "start": 609.72,
      "end": 614.94,
      "text": "내가 다른 일을 하느라 시간을 그렇게 보내지 않았을 거란 말이죠. 라는 말입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 615.74,
      "end": 620.72,
      "text": "엄마가 아픈 줄 알았다면 내가 다른 일에 집중하지도 않았을 거예요. 이 말이 되겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 620.72,
      "end": 627.92,
      "text": "She would have focused on her relationship with her mom, and not her work, and marriage, getting married to that guy, and Jonathan."
    },
    {
      "start": 627.92,
      "end": 631.64,
      "text": "저는 특히 이 마지막 대사가 굉장히 여운에 남았었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 631.82,
      "end": 634.4,
      "text": "I feel how much she loved her mom, Teresa."
    },
    {
      "start": 634.64,
      "end": 635.3,
      "text": "You can feel it."
    },
    {
      "start": 635.32,
      "end": 635.56,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 636.28,
      "end": 638.98,
      "text": "정말 진정한 사랑을 많이 느낀 장면이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 639.46,
      "end": 640.86,
      "text": "이 장면 한 번 더 들어보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 640.86,
      "end": 642.78,
      "text": "Why didn't you tell me yourself?"
    },
    {
      "start": 643.18,
      "end": 643.98,
      "text": "You were lying."
    },
    {
      "start": 644.16,
      "end": 646.48,
      "text": "Every minute you knew, and you didn't tell me."
    },
    {
      "start": 646.54,
      "end": 647.04,
      "text": "I'm sorry."
    },
    {
      "start": 647.71,
      "end": 648.85,
      "text": "I didn't want to make you sad."
    },
    {
      "start": 648.99,
      "end": 651.17,
      "text": "You didn't think I'd be sad if you just died one day?"
    },
    {
      "start": 651.37,
      "end": 651.75,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "start": 651.93,
      "end": 652.31,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.91,
      "end": 654.37,
      "text": "I didn't want anything to change."
    },
    {
      "start": 655.09,
      "end": 655.89,
      "text": "Maybe I was wrong."
    },
    {
      "start": 655.89,
      "end": 661.06,
      "text": "I knew that you were dying, I wouldn't have spent my time doing other stuff."
    },
    {
      "start": 661.06,
      "end": 669.84,
      "text": "네, 여운이 맴도는 순간이긴 하지만 우리 청취자분 메시지로 분위기를 좀 업 하고 마무리해 볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 669.94,
      "end": 670.6,
      "text": "Yes, please."
    },
    {
      "start": 671.74,
      "end": 672.66,
      "text": "5687님."
    },
    {
      "start": 673.06,
      "end": 674.88,
      "text": "우리 딸이 미국인이랑 사귄대요."
    },
    {
      "start": 675.1,
      "end": 678.24,
      "text": "어쩌면 저도 미국 사위가 생길지도 모릅니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 678.44,
      "end": 678.68,
      "text": "크크."
    },
    {
      "start": 679.22,
      "end": 683.38,
      "text": "동부 출신이라서 크리스쌤과 좀 다를 것 같긴 하지만."
    },
    {
      "start": 683.54,
      "end": 683.76,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 683.98,
      "end": 686.36,
      "text": "암튼 크서방이 더 가깝게 느껴지네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 686.36,
      "end": 686.92,
      "text": "아, 네."
    },
    {
      "start": 687.78,
      "end": 689.3,
      "text": "네, 당장 헤어지라고 하고."
    },
    {
      "start": 690.48,
      "end": 691.62,
      "text": "서부 남자랑 가요."
    },
    {
      "start": 692.14,
      "end": 693.54,
      "text": "한국 남자랑 가든가."
    },
    {
      "start": 694.14,
      "end": 698.64,
      "text": "아휴, 이런 대답을 해 주실 줄은 전혀 예상을 못해가지고 당황스러웠네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 698.84,
      "end": 699.32,
      "text": "I'm just kidding."
    },
    {
      "start": 699.7,
      "end": 700.06,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 700.06,
      "end": 701.08,
      "text": "I'm sure he's a great guy."
    },
    {
      "start": 701.54,
      "end": 704.2,
      "text": "Yes, East Coast men are different from West Coast men."
    },
    {
      "start": 704.4,
      "end": 706.76,
      "text": "Generally, but that's also a stereotype."
    },
    {
      "start": 707.0,
      "end": 709.28,
      "text": "They can both be loving and lovable."
    },
    {
      "start": 709.6,
      "end": 713.38,
      "text": "So if you like him and your daughter loves him, then go for it."
    },
    {
      "start": 713.44,
      "end": 714.5,
      "text": "와우, 들으셨죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 715.02,
      "end": 715.46,
      "text": "화이팅!"
    },
    {
      "start": 715.46,
      "end": 718.44,
      "text": "네, 좋은 분이시기를 응원하도록 하겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 719.32,
      "end": 723.22,
      "text": "그러고 보니까 우리 next week에는 we're going to watch a new movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 723.4,
      "end": 724.32,
      "text": "A brand new movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 725.02,
      "end": 726.1,
      "text": "It's called The Seagull."
    },
    {
      "start": 726.36,
      "end": 728.28,
      "text": "Seagull 하면 갈매기 아니에요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 728.62,
      "end": 729.12,
      "text": "그러게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 729.24,
      "end": 729.34,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 729.58,
      "end": 730.6,
      "text": "끼룩끼룩 갈매기?"
    },
    {
      "start": 730.7,
      "end": 731.3,
      "text": "갈매기?"
    },
    {
      "start": 731.4,
      "end": 732.7,
      "text": "뭐 갈매기 쌀?"
    },
    {
      "start": 732.98,
      "end": 734.08,
      "text": "이런 거 생각이 나는데."
    },
    {
      "start": 734.98,
      "end": 736.66,
      "text": "아, 정말 반전의 사나이."
    },
    {
      "start": 737.02,
      "end": 738.92,
      "text": "What's it going to be about?"
    },
    {
      "start": 739.12,
      "end": 739.54,
      "text": "그러게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 739.56,
      "end": 741.38,
      "text": "I can't predict what it's going to be about."
    },
    {
      "start": 741.38,
      "end": 742.0,
      "text": "오, 네."
    },
    {
      "start": 742.1,
      "end": 745.52,
      "text": "갈매기 쌀에 관련된 것일지, 갈매기에 관련된 것일지."
    },
    {
      "start": 745.64,
      "end": 746.04,
      "text": "다음 영화가."
    },
    {
      "start": 746.04,
      "end": 746.52,
      "text": "Shrimp chips인가."
    },
    {
      "start": 746.84,
      "end": 747.96,
      "text": "오, 기다려집니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 748.38,
      "end": 749.76,
      "text": "아, 우리 see you next week."
    }
  ]
}